: : Kup : :
Kup runs after Cam and Windlord. What a mess this was. He stops at the entrance when he sees that Windlord has calmed her down. He holds the vaccine.
Kup: She is still going to need this.
 raccoon7679 <raccoon7679@...> wrote:Cam::

She ran down the duct and around in the ventilation system.  She 
finally found one to the outside. She could see daylight coming 
through it.  She back up and tried to ram it, but she was too small 
to move it.  A loud bang could be heard through out the docking 
levels and in the enginering rooms.  She tried again and again, but 
the vent cover would not move.  She sighed and went around looking 
for another vent.  She found one and hoped this one would let her 
out.  She Rammed it at full speed.  The vent cover gave way. She fell 
50 feet to the ground.  She rolled and landed in a big shrub.  She 
lay there, dazed for a few minuted. "uhhhh, that didn't feel good 
mom." she said in a soft voice. She got up and started limping in fox 
mode away from the base.  She got to the main perimeter when she 
limped into the force field they had up to protect them from the 
plague.  She started to cry. "I just gotta get out of here. I must 
keep them safe."  She looked up at the sky. "I'm trying momma. I 
really am. I'm trying."  She looked around and started to dig in 
hopes of digging under the field.
